friendLines.title: Hello
friendLines.description: Tada! *giggles* Barbara is here~ Leave the healing to me, I will not disappoint you!

friendLines.title: Chat: Sleepiness
friendLines.description: *yawn* All this standing around is making me so sleepy...

friendLines.title: Chat: Encouragement
friendLines.description: Everyone is working super hard, we should be too!

friendLines.title: Chat: Keeping One Refreshed
friendLines.description: Are you tired? Try my new spicy energy drink, I'm sure it'll wake you up!

friendLines.title: When It Rains
friendLines.description: Don't stay out in the rain for too long, you'll catch a cold!

friendLines.title: When Thunder Strikes
friendLines.description: Whoa!

friendLines.title: When It Snows
friendLines.description: Ooh, snowflakes! Look at them dance!

friendLines.title: When the Sun Is Out
friendLines.description: This weather is so amazing! I could burst into song.

friendLines.title: When the Wind Is Blowing
friendLines.description: Don't worry! I will not... be blown away!

friendLines.title: Good Morning
friendLines.description: Morning~ Let's do our best today.

friendLines.title: Good Afternoon
friendLines.description: Oh? You want to hear me sing...? Sorry, the show is... It hasn't started yet.

friendLines.title: Good Evening
friendLines.description: I really want to eat some spicy squid at Good Hunter... but my stomach, er... Never mind...

friendLines.title: Good Night
friendLines.description: We had a great day today! Get some rest.

friendLines.title: About Barbara
friendLines.description: "To the wind that guides me: When I'm exhausted, bless me with the strength to keep going forward. When I'm uncertain, bless me with the wisdom to distinguish good from evil. When I suffer from injustice, bless me with the courage to fight back..." ...Oops, my apologies, I was just doing my prayers. *giggles* You need something?

friendLines.title: About Us: Hopes
friendLines.description: My dream is to bring a smile to the faces of all the people in my life! As long as I can help you on your journey, I'm happy~

friendLines.title: About Us: Dreams
friendLines.description: Thank you for being with me for all this time, I can feel that I'm getting closer to my dream. Hope we can keep this up in the future~!

friendLines.title: About the Vision
friendLines.description: Everyone has their own desires. To bring together and fulfill those desires and make everyone happy — that is the purpose my Archon has bestowed upon me.

friendLines.title: Something to Share
friendLines.description: I could never get bored of the breathtakingly beautiful nature that surrounds Mondstadt. I've heard that there are blue trees that exist by the sea shore near Inazuma City. I just need to save up a little more, and... What's that? You want to know what I'm saving up for? *chuckles* That's my little secret.

friendLines.title: Interesting Things
friendLines.description: Sunflowers always face the sun. They're so bright. In fact, my mother sent me a sunflower-style dress... I wonder when I'll finally get to wear it on stage?

friendLines.title: About Jean
friendLines.description: Acting Grand Master... Leader of the Knights of Favonius... Everyone seems to like her a lot. Oh? Me? I... Of course I have nothing but admiration for her!

friendLines.title: About Lisa
friendLines.description: I always take good care of Lisa. If she ever wants to become a star, she'll have my unconditional support, I'll cheer at the top of my lungs until my voice goes hoarse... Hmm, that might scare off her other fans though...

friendLines.title: About Amber
friendLines.description: I've seen Amber rushing out of Mondstadt on a mission countless times. Being an Outrider doesn't look easy.

friendLines.title: About Diluc
friendLines.description: Oh, Master Diluc? Last time, when I was performing at Angel's Share, he kept frowning... Maybe he doesn't like my singing?

friendLines.title: About Venti
friendLines.description: Venti's voice is amazing! But all the songs he sings and the ones I'm good at are very different. I tried to learn them but... the melodies are just so complicated.

friendLines.title: About Bennett
friendLines.description: Bennett always comes to the cathedral covered in scrapes and bruises... Though it clearly never bothers him a bit, given the big grin he always has on his face. He really should take better care of himself.

friendLines.title: About Varka
friendLines.description: My father left on the expedition with Grand Master Varka... I hope they are okay. Oh, what am I worried about? The Grand Master is none other than the Knight of Boreas, of course they will be fine! Still, I will be sure to pray for their safe return.

friendLines.title: About Rosaria
friendLines.description: Sister Rosaria is hard to get to know, especially given she never joins in on prayers, but... Oh, I'm sure she believes in the Anemo Archon! Although, I still don't really have the courage to try to talk to her...

friendLines.title: About Noelle
friendLines.description: Noelle is just the cutest! She's so kind and patient, you just feel totally relaxed when you're around her. ...Oh yeah, and she makes the tastiest snacks! Best part is, they're also healthy. Hehehe!

friendLines.title: More About Barbara: I
friendLines.description: Knights look so cool when they swing their sword in combat! Don't you think so? I tried using a sword before but... *sigh* Uh, let's just say I have zero talent with a sword.

friendLines.title: More About Barbara: II
friendLines.description: I want to heal everyone. This simple thought was all the motivation I needed to become a Deaconess. As long as I'm able to help everyone, I'll be content.

friendLines.title: More About Barbara: III
friendLines.description: Being an idol, I learned from Alice that "A true idol should always try to heal the soul of the people..." Yes, I completely agree.

friendLines.title: More About Barbara: IV
friendLines.description: I'm doing my best everyday... I hope my efforts earn the trust of the people of Mondstadt.

friendLines.title: More About Barbara: V
friendLines.description: Every time I get on stage I always start to doubt myself — can I really heal every person in Mondstadt? But I look at you now, and I feel that as long as we keep marching forward, maybe one day I might just— Huh? I've already healed you? Well, one's not enough! I've already healed a lot of people? I suppose...

friendLines.title: Barbara's Hobbies
friendLines.description: The smiles on the faces of the people I've helped keeps me going.

friendLines.title: Barbara's Troubles
friendLines.description: My companions keep getting injured, but I'm unable to share the burden of their pain. The only thing I can do is my absolute very best to heal their wounds! I'll make sure that everyone is healthy.

friendLines.title: Favorite Food
friendLines.description: Do you like spicy dried fish? I have two in my bag. Here, have one!

friendLines.title: Least Favorite Food
friendLines.description: I don't like anything bitter, especially... ugh, bitter gourd.

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: I
friendLines.description: It's a rare pleasure to eat food that suits my tastes so well. Today is a blessed day! Hehehe.

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: II
friendLines.description: Thank you for cooking these for me. This time around, you are the one healing me!

friendLines.title: Receiving a Gift: III
friendLines.description: Oh, uh, oh dear...

friendLines.title: Birthday
friendLines.description: Here you go! This is the gift I got for your birthday, along with my exclusive autograph! Hehe, when my next song comes out, I'll make sure you're the first one to hear it! Happy birthday!

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Intro
friendLines.description: A dance from Barbara, to bring you more healing!

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Building Up
friendLines.description: Aw, thank you so much for your support! Oh no, I'm too excited, my heart just can't stop racing!

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Climax
friendLines.description: Please, tell me how I can be stronger! Just leave it up to you? No, no, that won't do! I want to help too!

friendLines.title: Feelings About Ascension: Conclusion
friendLines.description: Traveling with you, I have discovered that the world is my stage! Thank you so much! *giggles* Ok! Let's shout it out one more time! Three, two, one — Go Barbara, go!

actionLines.title: Elemental Burst: III
actionLines.description: Come on, we can do it!

actionLines.title: Opening Treasure Chest: I
actionLines.description: This is the kind of surprise I could sing about.

actionLines.title: Opening Treasure Chest: III
actionLines.description: Hmm hmm hmm♪ Things are going so smoothly today~

actionLines.title: Low HP: II
actionLines.description: I can't stop now, they need me!

actionLines.title: Ally at Low HP: I
actionLines.description: I don't want to see you hurt...

actionLines.title: Ally at Low HP: II
actionLines.description: Please, let me tend to your wounds!
